Thanks, Stephen, and all...That indeed is what I was looking for!  
 @Nick: I thought that was indeed disgusting, but I thought it was devilishly clever of her as well. She was playing the part of a reclusive tragedy writer who seemed to have no penchant for public display. I thought the spitting, while putrid, was fitting.

\*\*\*\*...Reminds me of Michael Scott in the American version of The Office: “I would never have called Oscar faggy had I known he was gay. You don’t call retarded people “retards”. That would be in bad taste. You call your friends “retards” when they’re acting retarded. And I consider Oscar to be my friend.”
